data.title: B Tree To B Tower Support / Info ZERO/POINT
data.description: Here's a great support ZERO/POINT lineup for B Tower from B Tree. Unless you have a reason to; try to time the ZERO/POINT so that you gather information with it, and make it more difficult for enemy players in B Tower to help their teammates defend B as your team pushes into Site.
